channel.description:
This is and will be a new generation in runescape private servers. So to start... My name is Ty i am age 15 and i am co owner with 2 other guys jake and luke. We are dedicated staff and ready to go to the top! We started this project about a week ago and have been adding on to things with our little bit of coding knowledge. Also our coder Jake has not done a whole lot yet. What we are trying to accomplish will take tons of time lots of people and talent! A few things the server already has: Two custom minigames A few customs Corp Barrelchest ect... Staff List: Owner: -Ty (cashmoney516) -Jake -Luke Admins: -Nyuu -N I B -none (more spots) Mods: -Chris6564 -none -none -none (more spots) What i am looking for: Head Coders: (will get owner and is the best of best coders from the group) - None - None Major Coders: (will get admin ingame and the runners up for Head Coders) -Zach -None -None Minor Coders: (everyone else) -iiPod (client) [google] -none -none -none (ect...) Goals for the server: -100% working pyamid plunder -After our 317 is out we will also have a 500+ -100% soul wars -100% dueling (we have it at maybe 50-85%) -A vast amount of players and staff. -Extreme Pots -Have a full team and recreate map data and everything -Have custom real Runescape models added to the server -Lower XP rate just a bit faster then rs so you stay active. Much more! Much more great ideas on this server So far we are a Ryanscape base and we are in our minor beta stages of release. Nothing major yet well be working on it all soon. Have fun Hope you enjoy. If you would like more information pm me or add me on msn: cash.money516@live.com We will not steal peoples work this will be 100% our work other then whats already in the source and client. ~~~Pictures of whats in server MY FAVORITE!~~ -Customs [IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/Bandoswhip.png[/img][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/BarrelChestAnc.png[/img][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/Dclaws.png[/img][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/DragonHai.png[/img][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/GhostGuthans.png[/img][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/Maul.png[/img][IMG]http://i213.photobucket.com/albums/cc223/CrazyAmerican1/Pvps.png[/img] Things in this order Bandos whip, Barrelchest anchor, Dragon Claes, DragonHai, Ghost Guthans, a special Maul, and all Ancient armors.
